<%# One section: a uniform <details> summary bar + optional body. The layout
    is identical for every block kind; components only provide title/open/blocks.
    A body-less section (message/verifier title) is "static" — same summary bar,
    twisty hidden, nothing to toggle. %><details class="sec <%= section.name %><%= " err" if section.error %><%= " static" if section.header? %>"<%= " open" if section.open %>><summary><%= section.title %></summary><% unless section.header? %><div class="sec-body"><% Array(section.blocks).each do |b| %><%= render_content_block(b) %><% end %></div><% end %></details>